倍的不满，在很多看到了这篇文章的中国网民看来相当“难得”——尽管报道事实本就该是一家新闻媒体的应有之义。"},"attached_info":"ClUIg//bkuCGvtoHEAMaCDgyODQzOTc2IIf3qZYGMAs43ARABXIJNTQyNTI4NTY5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y","detail_text":"284 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-13a30c907591df36fe55f23cb0bfde92_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"6_1657516895.9266","card_id":"Q_542081040","target":{"id":542081040,"title":"当人脑完全开发时有多牛逼?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/542081040","type":"question","created":1657197900,"answer_count":119,"follower_count":334,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5633,23429,2008294],"comment_count":26,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"爱因斯坦的脑子据说只开发了10%，爱因斯坦已经这么牛逼了，那当人脑全部开发的时候有多牛逼。"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ig//bkuCGvtoHEAMaCDgyNzQ0MzY5IMyqm5YGMBo4zgJABnIJNTQyMDgxMDQweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"280 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-ab6c0b492a2c924cfdbc84c042520d22_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1657516895.9274037","card_id":"Q_538182545","target":{"id":538182545,"title":"江南七怪教了郭靖10年，为何还不如洪七公教一个月？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/538182545","type":"question","created":1655453589,"answer_count":122,"follower_count":192,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[23433],"comment_count":9,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"说起《射雕英雄传》，想必大家已经不陌生了，即便是没有看过原著的人，也大都看过电视剧，特别是83版，也就是黄日华和翁美玲出演的那一版，最为经典。我上一次看这部剧的时候，已经是10年前了，虽然时隔已久，但里面很多情节，我至今依然还记得。 特别是里面关于郭靖从一个只有三脚猫功夫的小白，到拥有降龙十八掌的大侠的转变，更是让我记忆犹新。而这其中有一个问题不知道大家有没有关注到！ 那就是，郭靖从小时候就跟着江南七怪学武功，但学了十余年，却没啥大的长进，而洪七公只教了他一个月，就变得非常厉害，这到底是为何呢？"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ig//bkuCGvt